===============================================================================
            Plugin for connect CopterControl board to simulator.
===============================================================================

---------------------------------------
        Building
---------------------------------------

a) download and install:
    - MinGW 4.4
    - Qt 4.8
b) run:
    qmake
    mingw32-make

---------------------------------------
        Installing
---------------------------------------

a) Copy "CopterControl" from build location to simulator's "Plugin" folder.
b) Copy "lib\*.dll" from source tree to simulator's root folder.

---------------------------------------
        Configure plugin
---------------------------------------

"CopterControl\cc_plugin.ini"

    remote_host, remote_port - IP address and port of target
    local_host, local_port   - IP address and port of simulator

---------------------------------------
        Tools
---------------------------------------

"tools\udp_test" utility can be used for test connection.
